description: [``botocore``] Documentation updates for Visual Monitoring feature and other doc ticket fixes.
[``botocore``] The Amazon Chime SDK Identity APIs allow software developers to create and manage unique instances of their messaging applications.
[``botocore``] The Amazon Chime SDK Messaging APIs allow software developers to send and receive messages in custom messaging applications.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for agent status and hours of operation. For details, see the Release Notes in the Amazon Connect Administrator Guide.
[``botocore``] This release adds support to track when a bucket access key was last used.
